# 🏦 Banking Dashboard (Power BI)

## 📌 Project Overview

This project is a Banking Dashboard created using Microsoft Power BI to analyze customer and transaction data.

## 📊 Dataset

* Customers Data
* Transactions Data
  (Common column: CustomerID)

## 🎯 Objectives

* Analyze customer behavior
* Track transaction patterns
* Provide meaningful insights

## 📈 Visualizations Used

* Stack Column Chart
* Line Chart
* Stack Bar Chart
* Pie Chart
* Donut Chart
* Cards
* Slicers
* Map

## 🛠 Tools Used

* Microsoft Power BI
* CSV Files

## 🔗 Data Model

* One-to-Many relationship between Customers and Transactions using CustomerID

## 🧠 Insights

* Deposits are higher than withdrawals
* Some cities have higher balance
* Transaction trends vary over time

